Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryAddUserToGroup
Property.StringValue: INSERT INTO SmUserGroup (ID, UserID, GroupID) (SELECT DISTINCT CASE WHEN MAX(ID) IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE MAX(ID)+1 END, (SELECT UserID FROM SmUser WHERE Name = '%s'), (SELECT GroupID FROM SmGroup WHERE Name = '%s') FROM SmUserGroup)

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryNewGroup
Property.StringValue: INSERT INTO SmGroup (GroupID, Name %s) (SELECT DISTINCT CASE WHEN MAX(GroupID) IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE MAX(GroupID)+1 END, '%s' %s FROM SmGroup)

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryGetUserProps
Property.StringValue: Name, UserID, FirstName, LastName, TelephoneNumber, EmailAddress, Disabled, PIN, Mileage, PasswordData

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QuerySetPassword
Property.StringValue: UPDATE SmUser SET Password = '%s' WHERE Name = '%s'

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryAuthenticateUser
Property.StringValue: SELECT Name FROM SmUser WHERE Name = '%s' AND Password = '%s'

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryGetGroupMembers
Property.StringValue: SELECT smUser.Name FROM smUser, SmUserGroup, smGroup WHERE smUser.UserID=SmUserGroup.UserID AND SmUserGroup.GroupID=SmGroup.GroupID AND SmGroup.Name = '%s'

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryRemoveUserFromGroup
Property.StringValue: DELETE FROM SmUserGroup WHERE UserID = (SELECT UserID FROM SmUser WHERE Name = '%s') AND GroupID=(SELECT GroupID FROM SmGroup WHERE Name = '%s')

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryGetObjInfo
Property.StringValue: SELECT Name, 'User' FROM SmUser WHERE Name = '%s' UNION SELECT Name, 'Group' FROM SmGroup WHERE Name = '%s'

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryInitUser
Property.StringValue: SELECT Name FROM SmUser WHERE Name = '%s'

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryLookup
Property.StringValue: SELECT Name, 'User' AS Class FROM SmUser WHERE Name %s UNION SELECT Name, 'Group' AS Class FROM SmGroup WHERE Name %s ORDER BY Class

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryNewUser
Property.StringValue: INSERT INTO SmUser (UserID, Name %s) (SELECT DISTINCT CASE WHEN MAX(UserID) IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE MAX(UserID)+1 END, '%s' %s FROM SmUser)

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryGetGroups
Property.StringValue: SELECT SmGroup.Name from SmGroup, SmUser, SmUserGroup where SmUser.Name = '%s' and SmUser.UserID = SmUserGroup.UserID and SmGroup.GroupID = SmUserGroup.GroupID

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryIsGroupMember
Property.StringValue: SELECT ID FROM SmUserGroup WHERE UserID = (SELECT UserID FROM SmUser WHERE Name = '%s') AND GroupID = (SELECT GroupID FROM SmGroup WHERE Name = '%s')

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryEnumerate
Property.StringValue: SELECT Name, 'Group' AS Class FROM SmGroup ORDER BY Class

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryLookupUser
Property.StringValue: SELECT Name, 'User' AS Class FROM SmUser WHERE %s

Property.Name: CA.SM::ODBCQuery.QueryLookupGroup
Property.StringValue: SELECT Name, 'Group' AS Class FROM SmGroup WHERE %s
